com.hortonworks.registries.schemaregistry.serde.pull

Interface PullDeserializer<S,F>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - type to represent schema related information.
    F - type to represent a field in a schema.
    All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Resourceable

    public interface PullDeserializer<S,F>
extends Resourceable
    This is a pull based deserializer which deserializes the given payload and user can call hasNext() and next() methods to retrieve the parsed content.
